                "data": {
                    "view": "pub_theme::components.blocks.about.story",
                    "title": "Our Story",
                    "content": "Laravel Pizza Meetups was born from a simple idea: great developers deserve great pizza. What started as a small gathering of Laravel enthusiasts in 2020 has grown into a vibrant community spanning multiple cities worldwide.\n\nWe believe that the best learning happens over food and conversation. Our meetups combine technical discussions, hands-on workshops, and networking opportunities - all while enjoying delicious pizza.\n\nWhether you're a Laravel beginner or a seasoned expert, you'll find a welcoming community ready to share knowledge, answer questions, and celebrate your successes.",
